        {
            "_id": "nZFgHZXnO78HnnPP",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/action.svg",
            "name": "Befouled Body",
            "sort": 1000000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "passive"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Any water the sarcovalt touches becomes diseased with filth fever.</p><hr /><p><strong>Filth Fever</strong> (disease)</p>\n<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> @Check[fortitude|dc:23|traits:disease]</p>\n<p><strong>Onset</strong> [[/br 1d4 #days]]{1d4 days}</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1} (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Drained]{Drained 1} (1 day)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Drained]{Drained 2} (1 day)</p>"
